description:
The #Huawei Innovation & Intellectual Property Forum 2025's Top Ten Inventions awards showcased Huawei's next-generation SSD designed for ultra-high capacity and performance, enabling faster, more stable transfer of larger data volumes. In line with the theme of Advancing Innovation with Openness, it details how increasing usable space and boosting access speed can strengthen scenarios like banking data security and faster feedback in healthcare.

author: Huawei
description:
At #Huawei Innovation & Intellectual Property Forum 2025, the Top Ten Inventions awards spotlighted the Scale-Up Ultra-Large-Scale SuperPoD computing platform. By linking 384 chips into a Supernode with high-speed interconnects, it targets low latency and high throughput for AI workloads, even during peak demand.
